---
title: Pesto Mozzarella BLTs Serves 2 | on Toasty Bread
description: We've updated a classic lunch staple with the addition of creamy, melted mozzarella and fragrant basil pesto. Juicy tomatoes, crispy bacon and toasty bread make it the cozy lunch you deserve.
